Privacy Policy for Apps Develeoped by Lighting Studio
It is Lighting Studio Appsâ€™ policy to respect your privacy regarding any information we may collect while operating our website and while the App is being used. Accordingly, we have developed this privacy policy in order for you to understand how we collect, use, communicate, disclose and otherwise make use of personal information. We have outlined our privacy policy below.
1.Security
Basically, we don't collect any information or data about our users. All user's works and data are stored locally in the app.
1.1 We won't upload your photos
All photos and videos taken by the user are stored locally on the phone. We do not upload or analyze users' photos.
1.2 We don't analyze and collect your face data
Privacy is very important to our user. We do not analyze and collect face data in photos and videos.
1.3 Information Collection and Use
We will collect personal information by lawful and fair means and, where appropriate, with the knowledge or consent of the individual concerned.
When a user sends us a feedback email, it will include the user's email address. We will only use this information for the purpose of contacting with users and improving our services. We do not share this information with third parties. Nor will this information be used for marketing.
2.Contact Us
If you have any questions, suggestions about our products, or need technical support, please do not hesitate to contact me at
